nodes.name: ImageModel
nodes.class_name:
ImageModel(
  (blocks): ModuleList(
    (0): BasicConvBlock(
      (conv): Conv2d(1, 32, kernel_size=(5, 5), stride=(1, 1), padding=(2, 2))
      (relu): LeakyReLU(negative_slope=0.2)
      (batchnorm): BatchNorm2d(32, eps=1e-05, momentum=0.1, affine=True, track_running_stats=True)
      (pool): MaxPool2d(kernel_size=(2, 2), stride=(2, 2), padding=0, dilation=1, ceil_mode=False)
    )
    (1): BasicConvBlock(
      (conv): Conv2d(32, 32, kernel_size=(3, 3), stride=(1, 1))
      (relu): LeakyReLU(negative_slope=0.1)
      (batchnorm): BatchNorm2d(32, eps=1e-05, momentum=0.1, affine=True, track_running_stats=True)
      (pool): MaxPool2d(kernel_size=(2, 2), stride=(2, 2), padding=0, dilation=1, ceil_mode=False)
    )
    (2): BasicConvBlock(
      (conv): Conv2d(32, 10, kernel_size=(3, 3), stride=(1, 1))
      (relu): LeakyReLU(negative_slope=0.1)
      (batchnorm): BatchNorm2d(10, eps=1e-05, momentum=0.1, affine=True, track_running_stats=True)
      (pool): MaxPool2d(kernel_size=(2, 2), stride=(2, 2), padding=0, dilation=1, ceil_mode=False)
    )
    (3): BasicConvBlock(
      (conv): Conv2d(10, 5, kernel_size=(3, 3), stride=(1, 1))
      (relu): LeakyReLU(negative_slope=0.1)
      (batchnorm): BatchNorm2d(5, eps=1e-05, momentum=0.1, affine=True, track_running_stats=True)
      (pool): MaxPool2d(kernel_size=(2, 2), stride=(2, 2), padding=0, dilation=1, ceil_mode=False)
    )
    (4): BasicConvBlock(
      (conv): Conv2d(5, 1, kernel_size=(2, 2), stride=(1, 1))
      (relu): LeakyReLU(negative_slope=0.1)
      (batchnorm): BatchNorm2d(1, eps=1e-05, momentum=0.1, affine=True, track_running_stats=True)
      (pool): MaxPool2d(kernel_size=(2, 2), stride=(2, 2), padding=0, dilation=1, ceil_mode=False)
    )
  )
  (Z): Linear(in_features=36, out_features=36, bias=True)
)

nodes.name: FeatureModel
nodes.class_name:
FeatureModel(
  (dnn_layers): ModuleList(
    (0): Linear(in_features=9, out_features=256, bias=True)
    (1): ReLU()
    (2): BatchNorm1d(256, eps=1e-05, momentum=0.1, affine=True, track_running_stats=True)
    (3): Linear(in_features=256, out_features=256, bias=True)
    (4): ReLU()
    (5): BatchNorm1d(256, eps=1e-05, momentum=0.1, affine=True, track_running_stats=True)
  )
  (output_layer): Linear(in_features=256, out_features=36, bias=True)
)
